The evidence with the title 'The president's Apology Tour - WSJ ' says Apr 23, 2009  ... By confessing our nation 's sins, White House press secretary Robert Gibbs said that mr. Obama has " changed the image of America around the world" and made the U.S. " safer and stronger." As evidence, mr. Gibbs pointed to the absence of protesters during the Summit Of The Americas this past weekend . 
